{"id":63949,"date":"2021-10-15T12:47:59","date_gmt":"2021-10-15T11:47:59","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=63949"},"modified":"2022-06-27T13:49:55","modified_gmt":"2022-06-27T11:49:55","slug":"gordes-france","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/gordes-france\/","title":{"rendered":"Gordes, France: The Icon of Provence"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">Things to do in Gordes<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Gordes has something for every kind of traveler. It&#x2019;s situated in the breathtaking nature of the Luberon Regional Park, looking down on the greenery of the French countryside. In July and August, you can also see the iconic purple <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/lavender-fields-provence\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">fields of lavender<\/a>! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095432\/gordes-france-09.jpg\" alt=\"lavender provence france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"lavender provence france\" class=\"wp-image-65229 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095432\/gordes-france-09.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095432\/gordes-france-09-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095432\/gordes-france-09-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095432\/gordes-france-09-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095432\/gordes-france-09-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/