ngs over the years. However, it&#x2019;s managed to preserve its ancient beauty.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/french-riviera-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The complete guide to the south of France<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084311\/gordes-france-5.jpg\" alt=\"gordes provence france view\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"gordes provence france view\" class=\"wp-image-64901 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084311\/gordes-france-5.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084311\/gordes-france-5-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084311\/gordes-france-5-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084311\/gordes-france-5-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084311\/gordes-france-5-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084311\/gordes-france-5-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084311\/gordes-france-5-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/