strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Opening Times and Entry Fee: <\/strong>The caves are open from the end of March until the beginning of November from 10 AM &#x2013; 6 PM (break for lunch 1.30 &#x2013; 2.30). The cost of entry is 6 EUR.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/63949&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14120702\/gordes-france-1-1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14120702\/gordes-france-1-1-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14120702\/gordes-france-1-1-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Gordes, France: The Icon of Provence\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-l-eglise-saint-fermin\">L&#x2019;Eglise Saint Fermin<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>L&#x2019;Eglise Saint Fermin is a beautiful church and a must-see on your trip to Gordes, France. Not only is it beautiful on the outside, but it has a spectacular interior. In fact, some have likened it to Italian churches because of its beautiful paintings and carvings. Inside, you&#x2019;ll find eight different chapels, each dedicated to a patron saint of another profession. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The church is an icon of the town and sits at one of the highest points in the village, making it a great place to go for views of the town.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084229\/gordes-france-1.jpg\" alt=\"gordes france village provence\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"gordes france village provence\" class=\"wp-image-64892 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084229\/gordes-france-1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084229\/gordes-france-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084229\/gordes-france-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084229\/gordes-france-1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084229\/gordes-france-1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084229\/gordes-france-1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084229\/gordes-france-1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084229\/gordes-france-1-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09084229\/gordes-france-1-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\