u&#x2019;ve finished exploring the castle, walk a little bit further up to the hill to another brilliant viewing area.&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Entrance fee and opening times:<\/strong> 7 EUR. The castle is open every day from 10 AM &#x2013; 6 PM<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14100828\/gordes-france-011.jpg\" alt=\"Chateau du Gordes France\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"Chateau du Gordes France\" class=\"wp-image-65237 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14100828\/gordes-france-011.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14100828\/gordes-france-011-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14100828\/gordes-france-011-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14100828\/gordes-france-011-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14100828\/gordes-france-011-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14100828\/gordes-france-011-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14100828\/gordes-france-011-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content