om Monday &#x2013; Saturday 10.30, 14.00, 15.00, 16.00. Sunday &#x2013; 14.00, 15.00, 16.00<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.senanque.fr\/en\/visits-of-the-abbey-2-2\/\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your visit here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095514\/gordes-france-08.jpg\" alt=\"gordes provence lavender\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"gordes provence lavender\" class=\"wp-image-65231 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095514\/gordes-france-08.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095514\/gordes-france-08-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095514\/gordes-france-08-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095514\/gordes-france-08-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095514\/gordes-france-08-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095514\/gordes-france-08-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095514\/gordes-france-08-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/