>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Day Tour: <\/strong>Alternatively, you can join a day tour to Gordes from bigger cities in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/provence-things-to-do\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Provence<\/a>. These include a tour guide and return transport.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/luberon-villages-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book a half-day tour to the villages.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"besttime\">Best Time to Visit<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Gordes is an icon of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/provence-things-to-do\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Provence<\/a> and, as a result, gets busy in the summer months. However, it&#x2019;s the only time you&#x2019;ll be able to see the lavender fields burst into color, which is definitely a once-in-a-lifetime experience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you don&#x2019;t mind not seeing the lavender, it&#x2019;s a good idea to visit in the shoulder seasons. For example, spring and autumn are perfect with warm days and quieter streets.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/lavender-fields-provence\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Here are the best lavender fields in Provence<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095752\/gordes-france-10.jpg\" alt=\"best time to visit provence france lavender\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best time to visit provence france lavender\" class=\"wp-image-65233 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095752\/gordes-france-10.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095752\/gordes-france-10-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095752\/gordes-france-10-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095752\/gordes-france-10-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095752\/gordes-france-10-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095752\/gordes-france-10-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095752\/gordes-france-10-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095752\/gordes-france-10-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095752\/gordes-france-10-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095752\/gordes-france-10-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/14095752\/gordes-france-10-1152x144